Calcy.net

Scientific Calculator

This is an online javascript scientific calculator. You can click the buttons or type to perform calculations as you would on a physical calculator.

Features trigonometric functions, logarithms, exponentials, memory operations, and full keyboard support.

 
0

You can use your keyboard for basic operations:

Numbers (0-9), operators (+, -, *, /), Enter (=), Escape (AC), Backspace

Frequently Asked Questions

Calculator Tips

  • • Use parentheses to control order of operations
  • • The calculator maintains a history of your last 10 calculations
  • • Scientific notation is used for very large or small numbers
  • • Memory functions persist until you clear them or refresh the page
  • • All trigonometric functions work with the selected angle mode
